Project Title: Simplified To-Do List

Description:
Taskify is a sleek and responsive to-do list website crafted using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. 
This project focuses on providing users with an intuitive interface for efficient task management. 
Users can effortlessly add, edit, and delete tasks, with dynamic updates facilitated by JavaScript. 
The design is clean, featuring deadline alerts, task categorization, and local storage for data persistence.
Taskify ensures a seamless experience across devices and browsers, promoting a hassle-free approach to staying organized and productive.





